  "description": "美國哲學家、詩人（1803－1882）",
  "bio": "拉爾夫·沃爾多·愛默生（英語：Ralph Waldo Emerson，1803年5月25日—1882年4月27日），生於波士頓，美國思想家、文學家。",
  "bio_source": "zhwiki",
  "description_en": "American philosopher (1803–1882)",
  "bio_en": "Ralph Waldo Emerson (May 25, 1803 – April 27, 1882), who went by his middle name Waldo, was an American essayist, lecturer, philosopher, minister, abolitionist, and poet who led the Transcendentalist movement of the mid-19th century. He was seen as a champion of individualism and critical thinking, as well as a prescient critic of the countervailing pressures of society and conformity.",
  "bio_en_source": "enwiki"
